HEADWORD: Sticky
<hw>Stick"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Stickier</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
<adjf>Stickiest</adjf>.]</amorph> <def>Having the quality of sticking to
a surface; adhesive; gluey; viscous; viscid; glutinous;
tenacious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Herbs which last longest are those of strong smell, and with a
<qex>sticky</qex> stalk.</q> <rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stiddy</ent>⟦br⟧
